column15:
The following post uses a Distort tactic:

@longword Like this now deleted post on the CPC website when O'Toole was their leader. It's all about Conservatives winning at any cost and most Canadian citizens will be the ones who pay the price. #NeverVoteConservative https://t.co/3BWZP6nwwc

This post distorts the main message by implying that the Conservative Party of Canada is willing to win at any cost and that most Canadian citizens will suffer as a result. This distortion aims to paint the CPC in a negative light and influence public opinion against them.

